INTRO                                             You see a man wondering the dungeon. He has the aspect of one with secrets on   his mind. He watches keenly as you approach.                                                                            NAME                                              "Jake. A good day to you, sir."                                                                                                                                                                         JOB                                               "My job? 'Tis hard to say. I am but a wonderer, much like yourself. In my       travels I hath learned of a powerful ITEM."                                                                             BYE                                               "Good day."                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               "Hmm. Don't know."                                                                                                                                                                                      ITEM                                              "Well, I canst say much to thee yet. Thou might speak with Tom on level 2. Make sure you use the PASSWORD."                                                                                             PASSWORD                                          "We artifact hunters are always careful!" He smiles. "When you see Tom, just    say ZAZA to him. He will then know thou hast spoken with me."                                                           ZAZA                                              "Yes, zaza. That is all."                                                                                                                                                                               